        <br /><br />
        <h5>Selecting your team</h5><br><img src="/images/content/30/basics1.jpg" align="right">
        Naruto-Arena.com focuses on tactics and team strategies. Selecting the right team is an essential part of the <a
            href='/game-manual/' class="con" name="game">game</a>. You are going to create and form teams of three <a
            href='/characters-and-skills/' class="con" name="characters">characters</a>. These <a
            href='/characters-and-skills/' class="con" name="characters">characters</a> should be able to work well
        together, based on chakra requirement and how some <a href='/characters-and-skills/' class="con"
            name="skills">skills</a> may back eachother up. While playing the <a href='/game-manual/' class="con"
            name="game">game</a> you will see different strategies done by different teams. Your task is to <a
            href='/search/' class="con" name="find">find</a> the best tactic and train yourself into how to pull it off.
        <br /><br />
